The '''Hyabb-Twith Corridor''' was an ancient [[Hyperspace route/Legends|hyperspace trade route]] that was located on the spinward arc of the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Galactic Core]]. The route connected the [[Planet/Legends|planets]] [[Hyabb]] and [[Twith]], passing through [[Voon/Legends|Voon]] in the process.

==History==
In the decades prior to the [[Old Sith Wars]] this route was in contended territory, and there was a constant threat attacks from the warring factions. This situation was made worse when the [[Nelori Marauders]] decide to begin raiding ships along the route, this continued until the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] were called in to defuse the situation.

